    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和沃尔兹计划在辩论后访问竞争激烈的摇摆州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/harris-walz-plan-post-debate-tour-of-swing-states-in-tight-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将在周二与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论后前往仍然激烈的战场州，一项民意调查显示，这位前总统在全国范围内领先，许多选民表示他们需要更多地了解哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/harris-walz-plan-post-debate-tour-of-swing-states-in-tight-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坦桑尼亚总统下令调查选举前绑架事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/tanzania-president-orders-probe-into-pre-election-abductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坦桑尼亚总统萨米亚·苏鲁胡·哈桑下令对该国即将举行的选举前政治人物和政府批评人士的绑架事件进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/tanzania-president-orders-probe-into-pre-election-abductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院对阿富汗撤军的调查将延续至大选之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/house-probe-into-afghanistan-pullout-to-extend-beyond-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责调查的一位议员表示，众议院共和党人将把对美国撤军阿富汗的为期两年的调查延长至周一发布的报告之后，并持续到 11 月“大选结束后很长一段时间”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/house-probe-into-afghanistan-pullout-to-extend-beyond-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔及利亚总统在初步选举结果中以压倒性优势获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/algerian-president-wins-by-a-landslide-in-initial-vote-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔及利亚总统阿卜杜勒马吉德·特本准备连任，初步结果显示他以压倒性优势获胜。批评人士称，此次选举比预期提前举行，是为了排挤任何强劲竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/algerian-president-wins-by-a-landslide-in-initial-vote-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界主要碳排放国称新气候谈判取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/world-s-top-carbon-emitters-cite-progress-in-new-climate-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京举行的为期三天的会谈中，美国和中国谈判代表讨论了遏制森林砍伐和减少严重的全球变暖污染等共同目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/world-s-top-carbon-emitters-cite-progress-in-new-climate-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的内布拉斯加州突然成为政治战场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/trump-is-up-but-also-mixed-voter-tendencies-in-us-heartland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[内布拉斯加州不在任何人的选举年宾果卡上，但沃伦·巴菲特的家乡却迅速成为政党争夺国会控制权甚至白宫控制权的战场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/trump-is-up-but-also-mixed-voter-tendencies-in-us-heartland</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚总统称俄罗斯无人机在北约成员国拉脱维亚坠毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/russian-drone-crashes-in-nato-member-latvia-its-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，在乌克兰遭遇的另一场无人机连环袭击中，拉脱维亚和罗马尼亚分别报告了涉及俄罗斯无人机的事件，这表明该地区国家面临的空中威胁日益增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/russian-drone-crashes-in-nato-member-latvia-its-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 13:48:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾逮捕杜特尔特牧师，与马科斯矛盾加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/philippines-arrests-duterte-s-pastor-ally-wanted-by-fbi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局通缉的一名福音派传教士被捕，此人与前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特及其家人关系密切，而该家族与总统费迪南德·马科斯之间的裂痕正在加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/philippines-arrests-duterte-s-pastor-ally-wanted-by-fbi</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 11:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派领导人接到逮捕令后逃亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/venezuela-opposition-leader-flees-to-spain-after-arrest-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，对委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的抵抗力量遭受重大打击，总统的主要反对派逃往西班牙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/venezuela-opposition-leader-flees-to-spain-after-arrest-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊采取行动打击过度旅游和短期租赁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/greece-to-take-action-against-overtourism-short-term-leasing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在后疫情时代，游客数量持续创下新高，希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯宣布了旨在应对过度旅游负面影响的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-07/greece-to-take-action-against-overtourism-short-term-leasing</guid>
